# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Secrets - NEVER commit these. This repo is public.
# .env holds only the publishable/anon key (safe), but .secrets.env holds the
# service_role key, which bypasses Row Level Security on the entire database.
.secrets.env
*.secrets.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Supabase CLI link state. Local-only artifacts of `supabase link`, and
# pooler-url embeds connection details — keep them out of a public repo.
supabase/.temp/

# iOS code signing. The .cer and .certSigningRequest already sitting in the repo
# root are harmless on their own, but a .p12 export carries the private key and
# tends to land in the same folder. This repo is public — keep all of it out.
*.cer
*.certSigningRequest
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
*.p8

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
